<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmação de Cadastro</title>
    <style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #12111f;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}

.container {
    background-color: #11072c;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    color: #ffffff;
}

h1{
  color: blue;
}

form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
}

label {
    font-weight: bold;
}

input[type="text"],
input[type="text"],
input[type="email"],
input[type="password"] {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 8px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

button {
    background-color: blue;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #e49c01;
}

p{
  text-align: center;
}

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Confirmação de Cadastro</h1>
        <h4>Se os dados estiverem corretos, faça seu login abaixo</h4>
        <div id="userInfo"></div>

      
      <p> <a href='login'>FAÇA SEU LOGIN AQUI</a></p>
      
    </div>

    <script src="script2.js"></script>

    </script>
</body>

</html>